{"tid":1706273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］有無諗過唔好再係連登 IG到叫人出去？","createTime":"2019-11-11T04:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T06:53:39.000Z","uid":31335,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f57e72ce48286af0a729458844f5c17c2a82b385","tid":1706273,"uid":31335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"今日十點幾有人提議中環［和你食］<br />\n但一到lunch time我地偉大既警察已經重兵駐守左仲趕人走<br />\n其實係因為每次係到吹雞 班狗都會第一時間知 之後進行部署<br />\n<br />\n我諗緊既係<br />\n我地可唔可以唔好係到吹雞<br />\n而係每次發起行動既時候 係以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人傳人既方式</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地可以搵自己信得過既朋友去傳開 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一傳十 十傳百</span></span>暗地裹傳開去 <br />\n<br />\n到時我地出黎就係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真。突擊</span></span>既效果 令班狗仔部署唔到<br />\n<br />\n當然未必好完善 但我只係想成個運動有進步 唔好再比人禁住黎屌<br />\n<br />\n有咩改善歡迎討論下"},{"pid":"0759f57893fee16a2a4fca7bec4ec49dd3c43d33","tid":1706273,"uid":31335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"69b6d75c4553306ea5e616b73c4fac7c1be5f96d","tid":1706273,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"講左好撚多個月"},{"pid":"1faf0b7ec9350fa7eca9fd7be45f1ac343d9413a","tid":1706273,"uid":31335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"d6332a56702f26b753db20bdd71c0d45a77e0f4d","tid":1706273,"uid":71160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"傻hi先用連登<br />\n全天候被mon住"},{"pid":"3428f24a36570407e92408db66cb0d58fbdcf6a0","tid":1706273,"uid":31335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69b6d75c4553306ea5e616b73c4fac7c1be5f96d","tid":1706273,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"講左好撚多個月"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"有冇實行過"},